      "rationale": "The screw and rod are modelled as continuum elastic-plastic solids (bilinear isotropic hardening). Frictional contact (μ=0.3) represents screw-rod interface. This model form is consistent with published literature for metallic implant constructs under quasi-static bending and is sufficient to capture the three QoIs."
    },
