      "rationale": "Testing was performed at a single compression-bending load configuration per ASTM F1717. Only one test condition was explored; variation in offset distance or load angle was not included. This limits the achieved level to 2, below the required level of 3. This gap is acknowledged and accepted given the standardized nature of F1717 and the medium model risk."
